{"tid":1605494,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"歷史討論 - 防守黎講最好係犄角之勢 - 如果我地要守住台北既西門國民小學一帶","createTime":"2019-09-30T10:02:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T05:11:20.000Z","uid":57633,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"082ea4fb5e2b5ad92a2b49594013ba8d8a7b5456","tid":1605494,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:02:12.000Z","msg":"犄角之勢係乜就唔詳講了<br />\n實例最出名都係襄陽城 同 樊城<br />\n阻擋左當時橫行天下既蒙古<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三國演義都有好多犄角之勢既例子 <br />\n<br />\n熱愛台灣既我<br />\n今日就想同大家討論下<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果實際要守台北既西門國民小學一帶, 我地應該點樣做</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n圖如下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/search/@25.0425445,121.5029396,18.04z\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fsearch%2F%4025.0425445%2C121.5029396%2C18.04z&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=2a26e5e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/search/@25.0425445,121.5029396,18.04z</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GbmWjaA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGbmWjaA.jpg&h=90f7e090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先守既地方要非死地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡單講即係要四通八達啦<br />\n分三隊<span style=\"color: green;\">綠A</span>, <span style=\"color: teal;\">藍B</span> 同<span style=\"color: purple;\">哨兵</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">綠A 要守係 昆明街 同 成都路 交界</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">藍B 要守係 康定路 同 內江街 交界</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">兩個紫色圈圈就放哨兵同傳訊兵</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">當藍B比攻既時候<br />\n如果對方一個方向既進攻, 咁守到緊係守啦<br />\n但當敵人係夾擊, 或者係猛攻<br />\n咁守唔到就要慢慢對住進攻既敵人1 2 1 2<br />\n慢慢退去另外兩個紫色圈圈<br />\n集中到一個方向為佳<br />\n不過兵方馬亂<br />\n成功退到是但一個圈都好好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n同時間, 紫色圈圈哨兵就要通知綠A班人準備<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">綠A班人準備乜???<br />\n誠如戰國四大名將所講 &quot;面對夾擊, 就用夾擊打回去&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(誤)</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/obLHeTK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FobLHeTK.jpg&h=d43de33c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對方只要攻過 <br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">左上紫圈 康定路 同 成都路 交界<br />\n右下紫圈 昆明街 同 內江街 交界</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">而藍B手足又開始守住紫圈</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">咁綠A手足就可以向住紫圈夾擊敵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"d991dd92e30a4f8c020730a2cdfb850729534167","tid":1605494,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:29:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>問題1 <br />\n如果今次比人攻既係綠A咁點?</strong></span><br />\n倒轉綠A同藍B角色咪得囉, 咁都問<br />\n.<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>問題2<br />\n綠A同藍B同時比人攻咁點?</strong></span><br />\n建議兩邊同時向後慢慢退去 <br />\n由守綠A同藍B 變守 兩個紫圈圈<br />\n繼續犄角<br />\n如果其中一邊敵人太前<br />\n仲可以考慮先夾擊一邊敵人先<br />\n.<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>問題3<br />\n敵人一開始就攻左紫圈先咪破解到?</strong></span><br />\n敵人入紫圈<br />\n你地都唔主動夾佢<br />\n我都唔知講咩好&hellip;"},{"pid":"4b1b8d4d8ebbfcbe979cb220b90adeabe09378de","tid":1605494,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:32:07.000Z","msg":"集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae76f1f7c1c4cee43c12688eff376b47bca5b28c","tid":1605494,"uid":297230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:34:56.000Z","msg":"Telegram 預設訊息可以保護到手足性命<br />\n希望大家可以幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCXiwqP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCXiwqP.png&h=5c04cb99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星火 TG: @Abccbbc<br />\n612 TG: @ReliefFund612<br />\nPush"}